760
00:45:22,352 --> 00:45:26,032
♪Don't waste time♪

761
00:45:26,722 --> 00:45:30,912
♪Back then, the road seemed ordinary♪

762
00:45:31,182 --> 00:45:35,052
♪Taste all the vicissitudes of life
in a flash♪

763
00:45:35,662 --> 00:45:39,802
♪Though nothing is permanent♪

764
00:45:40,382 --> 00:45:43,832
♪I wish you well♪
